575
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,190
There's gotta be a way.

576
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,070
Dad, take a look.

577
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:17,190
No need.

578
00:25:17,430 --> 00:25:18,310
Just tell me.

579
00:25:19,120 --> 00:25:20,590
There are lots of listed companies

580
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,350
seeking to buy private mines.

581
00:25:22,950 --> 00:25:25,310
If we manage to get this Zhifeng Group
to do their evaluation

582
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:27,470
on our mine before it's determined,

583
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:28,550
and finish the buyout,

584
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,070
we can avoid
a significant amount of losses.

585
00:25:31,550 --> 00:25:32,800
Good...

586
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:34,710
Do you know anyone from them?

587
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,550
No.

588
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,430
I bet your dad does.

589
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:41,590
I heard that Yu Zhifeng

590
00:25:41,710 --> 00:25:43,550
was from the Ministry of Mining.

591
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,880
I can't guarantee a sure success,

592
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,760
but I guess I can manage to jump in.

593
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,670
The top priority here is time.

594
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:56,550
I wish

595
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:58,640
we can meet this Mr. Yu sometime.

596
00:25:59,190 --> 00:26:00,000
Meet?

597
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:04,120
No, we shouldn't.

598
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,830
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

599
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:12,240
I'll be your middleman. Rest assured.

600
00:26:12,710 --> 00:26:13,590
No problem.

601
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,120
I trust you.

602
00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:19,760
Son,

603
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:24,160
our entire family

604
00:26:24,590 --> 00:26:25,640
relies on you now.

605
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:38,470
Hello, Mr. Chen?

606
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:49,590
Who... Who is this?

607
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:53,520
This is Yu Zhifeng from Zhifeng Group.

608
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:58,880
Nice to hear from you!

609
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:01,800
Fei Ke told me about your mine.

610
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:04,310
We've done some internal evaluation
and we think we can proceed.

611
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,830
The problem is,
there are other companies like yours.

612
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,880
Lately, with the tightening policies,

613
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:12,000
lots of companies
have been contacting us.

614
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:14,670
Honestly,

615
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,590
Nanlin's rating is not high enough.

616
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,280
Yes, I understand.

617
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,120
Had you approached us,

618
00:27:21,430 --> 00:27:22,640
we'd have offered a low price.

619
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,880
But Director General Li
was my superior before,

620
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:27,070
I'd owe him the favor.

621
00:27:28,430 --> 00:27:29,950
You... You don't say!

622
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:32,950
Director General Li
and I... are in-laws!

623
00:27:33,070 --> 00:27:34,240
In-laws!

624
00:27:34,710 --> 00:27:35,710
220 million.

625
00:27:35,830 --> 00:27:36,950
That's our best offer.

626
00:27:44,190 --> 00:27:45,190
But, um...

627
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,920
Can't... Can't you do more?

628
00:27:56,520 --> 00:27:57,550
Ask for 260.

629
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:59,240
He won't offer too much.

630
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:00,950
We're in a special condition.

631
00:28:10,470 --> 00:28:11,310
Well...

632
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,000
How about 260?

633
00:28:14,190 --> 00:28:15,950
That's a lucky number.

634
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:18,240
Deal!

635
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:52,430
Why use a talkie?

636
00:28:52,950 --> 00:28:54,000
There wouldn't be records.

637
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,520
So,

638
00:28:55,670 --> 00:28:56,830
what's caught on camera

639
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:59,310
wouldn't be able to prove
that you'd met Yu Zhifeng.

640
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:01,430
The room blocks cellphone signals.

641
00:29:01,430 --> 00:29:03,800
By doing so, you'd be clean
from illegal mining or rented accounts.

642
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,470
Fei Ke was meticulous

643
00:29:05,470 --> 00:29:06,640
and arranged things properly,

644
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,590
which is why I fell for his trick.

645
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:11,310
260 million is not a low price.

646
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:13,070
Shouldn't that solve the problem?

647
00:29:14,280 --> 00:29:15,670
If it could be solved that easily,

648
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:18,040
I wouldn't be here today.

649
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,920
What? How could he do that?

650
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,590
I thought we had a deal!

651
00:29:22,670 --> 00:29:25,280
Right when I thought I was saved,

652
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:28,520
Fei Ke told me
that Yu Zhifeng backed out.

653
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,880
He wanted 200 million.

654
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:31,670
In the end, Fei Ke said

655
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:34,400
that if I insisted on 260 million,

656
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:37,950
I'd have to pay Mr. Yu a 10% commission.

657
00:29:46,310 --> 00:29:47,950
[Chen Shufa]

658
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:50,400
Commission?

659
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,950
Can an owner from a listed company

660
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,160
do that?

661
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:55,240
That's not right.

662
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:57,280
Even if he wanted the money,

663
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,880
he wouldn't dare do it.

664
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,400
A deal that big...

665
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,350
went a bit too easily, don't you think?

666
00:30:04,550 --> 00:30:06,160
You wired all the money
to Fei Ke, didn't you?

667
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,470
Mr. Chen saw him as family

668
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:09,640
and trusted him entirely.

669
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,710
Under the emergency,

670
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:14,400
Fei Ke was his last resort.

671
00:30:14,800 --> 00:30:15,670
Right.

672
00:30:16,830 --> 00:30:18,590
He brain-washed me

673
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:21,160
into not daring to contact Yu Zhifeng

674
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:24,430
in case the deal went south.

675
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,640
He acted as the middleman.

676
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,920
And the fees

677
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:30,950
were wired to the account he designated.

678
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:33,400
Every time I asked him how things went,

679
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,830
he'd answer me the same thing.

680
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,310
Not yet, Dad.

681
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,040
Almost.

682
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:39,520
Maybe some more work
on the deputy general manager.

683
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,350
Not a lot.

684
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:41,640
Just wire it to me.

685
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,430
What?

686
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:46,920
Altogether, he took

687
00:30:47,590 --> 00:30:49,520
over 40 million from me.

688
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,920
And then he disappeared.

689
00:30:55,190 --> 00:30:56,240
Disappeared?

690
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:58,590
Gone! Out of thin air!

691
00:30:58,670 --> 00:31:00,950
All of a sudden!

692
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:01,800
I thought something happened to him

693
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:02,920
and I looked for him for a few days,

694
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:04,430
before I realized

695
00:31:04,430 --> 00:31:05,190
that he

696
00:31:05,710 --> 00:31:07,000
had run away with my money.

697
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,550
He was a fraud!

698
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,830
I thought you'd met Yu Zhifeng.

699
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:12,830
I have.

700
00:31:12,830 --> 00:31:14,160
Through a window glass.

701
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,400
It was blurry.

702
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,190
And when did you realize

703
00:31:17,190 --> 00:31:19,310
that Fei Ke was a fraud?

704
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:28,430
Open the door!

705
00:31:28,430 --> 00:31:29,400
Hello, sir. What can we help?

706
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,470
Sorry, but who are you looking for?

707
00:31:30,590 --> 00:31:32,070
Mr. Fei!

708
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:32,800
Fei Ke!

709
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,400
I'm sorry, sir,

710
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,590
but we don't have a Mr. Fei here.

711
00:31:34,590 --> 00:31:36,950
The subscriber you dialed
is not answered now.

712
00:31:37,710 --> 00:31:39,830
Fei Ke, where are you?

713
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:41,590
Pick up the phone, okay?

714
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,400
I'm Mr. Chen!

715
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:45,400
I'm one of your shareholders, remember?

716
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,120
Mr. Chen?

717
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:46,710
Hold on, please!

718
00:31:46,710 --> 00:31:48,430
I've invested money here!

719
00:31:48,430 --> 00:31:49,470
- I... I'm looking for Fei Ke.
- You can't go in!

720
00:31:49,470 --> 00:31:50,670
I'm a shareholder!

721
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:52,120
Sir, I'm afraid
we'll have to call security.

722
00:31:52,120 --> 00:31:52,880
We're calling security!

723
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,950
Fei Ke, if anything happens, talk to me.

724
00:31:54,950 --> 00:31:56,350
Don't do this to me, please!

725
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:04,520
Fei Ke!

726
00:32:10,350 --> 00:32:12,240
Fei Ke...

727
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:25,640
It's simple. Once I enter,

728
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,710
I'll go to the window.

729
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,400
When I give you the wave,

730
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:30,280
you can start your lines
with the walkie-talkie.

731
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,350
Have you memorized your lines?

732
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,310
Can you handle this?

733
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,950
Rest assured, bro.

734
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,040
So, today,

735
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:08,040
I'm recommending to you

736
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:10,800
this Da'an medical-grade
sphygmomanometer

737
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:13,590
with less
than three millimeters of error

738
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:14,590
and comprehensive features,

739
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:16,550
perfect for people above middle age.

740
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:18,830
An all-round strengthened arm belt.

741
00:33:19,310 --> 00:33:21,670
High-definition LED all-screen display.

742
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:23,470
All the data are clearly displayed.

743
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:25,710
1.5 thousand mA lithium-ion battery.

744
00:33:25,710 --> 00:33:27,190
Six hundred times of recharges.

745
00:33:27,430 --> 00:33:29,070
Enhanced with voice command.

746
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:02,670
Jiajia?

747
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:05,190
Jiajia, what's wrong?

748
00:34:08,910 --> 00:34:09,800
Jiajia!

749
00:34:10,470 --> 00:34:11,870
Answer me, Jiajia!

750
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:16,520
Jiajia!

751
00:34:17,240 --> 00:34:17,950
Where are you going?

752
00:34:19,560 --> 00:34:20,800
I wanna go look for Fei Ke!

753
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:23,280
Jiajia, calm down!

754
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,840
Wherever he is,

755
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,950
I will find him.

756
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:28,150
Don't be impulsive. You hear me?

757
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:29,710
Be good.

758
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,710
Be good. Wait for me at home.

759
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,760
Actually, government officials' profiles

760
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,110
are easily verified.

761
00:34:38,560 --> 00:34:41,080
Their information is semi-public.

762
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,560
We businessmen

763
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:44,080
are terrified of the officials.

764
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:45,840
We get scared when we see them,

765
00:34:45,870 --> 00:34:47,520
which makes us vulnerable.

766
00:34:47,910 --> 00:34:49,800
I only found out later

767
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:53,320
that this guy is audacious!

768
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,240
Sir...

769
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,800
Please! Please help me!

770
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,560
You're looking
for Deputy Director General Li, right?

771
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,470
You can talk to me. I'm his subordinate.

772
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,110
Hello, sir...

773
00:35:13,110 --> 00:35:13,800
Take... Take it easy.

774
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,080
Take your time.

775
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:17,470
You know, Mr. Li and I,

776
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,040
we're relatives.

777
00:35:20,390 --> 00:35:22,190
His son is my son-in-law.

778
00:35:22,190 --> 00:35:23,080
Your son-in-law?

779
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,430
Yes!

780
00:35:24,870 --> 00:35:25,470
We...

781
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:27,280
We're family!

782
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,520
I'm telling the truth. Look!

783
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:30,670
It's a wedding photo
of his son and my daughter.

784
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,870
This is my daughter. See?

785
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:33,190
This is his son.

786
00:35:35,390 --> 00:35:37,710
You... must be mistaken.

787
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:39,520
Well... What exactly do you want?

788
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:40,520
Why don't you just tell me?

789
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,240
I can't.

790
00:35:42,240 --> 00:35:43,150
I need to see him in person!

791
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:44,360
I need to tell him.

792
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,390
If you can't tell me,

793
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,600
I won't be able to help you.

794
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,280
Sir...

795
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,190
Don't go!

796
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:52,950
Sir...

797
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:54,360
- You don't have to call me sir.
- Fine, I'll tell you.

798
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:54,760
Go ahead.

799
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:56,710
His son told me that he could
help with the acquisition.

800
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:58,320
To buy my mining company.

801
00:35:58,470 --> 00:36:00,870
The buyer is Mr. Li's
former subordinate, Yu Zhifeng.

802
00:36:01,110 --> 00:36:01,800
You know him, right?

803
00:36:01,910 --> 00:36:02,950
He's the buyer.

804
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,040
Well, this is obviously a scam.

805
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:06,240
There's no such thing.

806
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:08,080
Besides, what you just mentioned,

807
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,150
acquisition and everything,

808
00:36:09,390 --> 00:36:10,320
they don't exist.

809
00:36:10,870 --> 00:36:11,760
And you know, the biggest problem is,

810
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,870
this son-in-law of yours

811
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,240
must be a mistake.

812
00:36:14,670 --> 00:36:16,040
Mr. Li doesn't even have a son.

813
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:16,870
That I can tell you for sure.

814
00:36:16,870 --> 00:36:17,430
But...

815
00:36:17,430 --> 00:36:18,320
Okay, no need for anything else.

816
00:36:18,670 --> 00:36:19,600
Don't believe in rumors

817
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:21,150
and don't spread them either.

818
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:23,110
All these things about business

819
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:25,430
and all the related policies

820
00:36:25,430 --> 00:36:26,520
are in fact public.

821
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:28,000
All you need to do

822
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:28,950
is check the official website.

823
00:36:29,320 --> 00:36:30,240
I've got a meeting.

824
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:30,710
Here.

825
00:36:30,710 --> 00:36:31,760
It's the card for our office.

826
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,190
You can call us if you have a question.

827
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,760
Any more problems, tell him,

828
00:36:34,870 --> 00:36:36,630
and they'll try to help you, okay?

829
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:37,600
Now, will you excuse me?

830
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:41,390
I'd suggest you call the police.

831
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,760
Jiajia, I'm home.

832
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:08,190
Jiajia?

833
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:10,470
Jiajia, I'm home.

834
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:12,040
Where are you?

835
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,080
Jiajia?

836
00:38:17,910 --> 00:38:22,950
♪The lights are on my wounds again♪

837
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:27,750
♪Not saying anything,
but feeling uneasy inside♪

838
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:31,710
♪Still pretending to be happy♪

839
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:38,470
♪I can't even blame you
for being so cruel♪

840
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:42,670
♪When you're lost and sad♪

841
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:47,470
♪I even don't have the right
to comfort you♪

842
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:52,990
♪I took a script
that has too many twists and turns♪

843
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:58,390
♪I can't either love or quit,
just pretending to smile♪

844
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:02,110
♪Who cares?♪

845
00:39:05,190 --> 00:39:09,070
♪I'm just an unneeded character♪

846
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:13,030
♪Like a role
that doesn't have a story to tell♪

847
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:19,110
♪Wait till the song is over
and everyone's gone♪

848
00:39:20,430 --> 00:39:24,030
♪I'm just an unneeded character♪

849
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:28,310
♪Like a puppet led by invisible strings♪

850
00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:33,950
♪Yet watched by your coldness♪

851
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:39,830
♪As my weary smile fades♪

852
00:39:40,830 --> 00:39:44,070
♪I can only be picked♪

853
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:47,430
